# Experiment Log – Transfer Attacks (Preliminary Results)

## Experiment Setup
- Task: Image Captioning Robustness Evaluation
- Attack Setting: Transfer-based attacks
- Attacks: FGSM, MI-FGSM
- Metric: BLEU
- Models Evaluated:
  - Original (Base) Model
  - LoRA Fine-tuned Model

---

## Results (BLEU Scores)

### Original Model

| Condition | BLEU |
|---------|------|
| Clean | 0.0303 |
| FGSM | 0.0243 |
| MI-FGSM | 0.0167 |

---

### LoRA Fine-tuned Model

| Condition | BLEU |
|---------|------|
