---

## Observations (Preliminary)

- Both models show degradation in caption quality under transfer attacks.
- MI-FGSM causes larger BLEU drop compared to FGSM.
- LoRA fine-tuning does not fully mitigate transfer-based adversarial effects.
- Further evaluation using METEOR and BERTScore is ongoing.

---

## Notes
- Results are preliminary and based on limited evaluation.
- Large-scale experiments and additional attacks will be included in future updates.
